elements.name: To verify whether system allows the user to navigate to the phone & Accessories page

steps.name: User is on the Amazon homepage
User navigate to Electronics and Computer > Phone and Accessories
User should see the "Phones & Accessories" page displayed

elements.name: To verify whether system allows the user to navigate to the SIM-Free & Unlocked Mobile Phones page

steps.name: User is on the phone accessories page
User click on SIM-Free under mobile phones section
User should see the page "SIM-Free & Unlocked Mobile Phones" displayed

elements.name: To verify whether system allows the user to list the samsung phone with specific specification

steps.name: User is on the SIM-Free & Unlocked Mobile Phones page
User click on Samsung under brands section
User click on Camera Resolution as "20" mp and above
User click on Model Year as "2023"
